title:
Discrete dynamics of phytoplankton-zooplankton systems with Holling type
  functional responses
abstract:
In this paper, we study discrete dynamics of phytoplankton-zooplankton system
with Holling type II and Holling type III predator functional responses. The
stability of positive fixed points are investigated. By finding invariant sets,
the convergence of the trajectory was shown under certain conditions on the
parameters.
